{"tid":1030313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片]暴力推跌女仔爆牙果位?!","createTime":"2019-02-21T00:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T07:35:32.000Z","uid":65346,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9b56f72a0a1adbcd9bcb5db45a1ee7980b7b6e4b","tid":1030313,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:42:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190220/59283899?fbclid=IwAR1lWvmlvISvkJpJt9YiglDdjkvLM0RGLkWdqzKnIukOpWqVsjbYd1vcgjM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F59283899%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1lWvmlvISvkJpJt9YiglDdjkvLM0RGLkWdqzKnIukOpWqVsjbYd1vcgjM&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=74b12ac7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F59283899%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1lWvmlvISvkJpJt9YiglDdjkvLM0RGLkWdqzKnIukOpWqVsjbYd1vcgjM&h=3cef0c18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190220/59283899?fbclid=IwAR1lWvmlvISvkJpJt9YiglDdjkvLM0RGLkWdqzKnIukOpWqVsjbYd1vcgjM</a><br />\n<br />\n【爆相爆片】大媽「虎尾腳」圖甩身 襲警被捕<br />\n<br />\n周二下午5時許，兩名警員在港鐵旺角站大堂向一名有濃厚鄉音的大媽查閱身份證，其間兩警被推撞，警員指着涉事大媽稱：「我而家拉你襲警！」大媽隨即激動反擊：「你擺明針對我，而家追賊呀？」警員反駁：「差人唔係俾你任打，我而家拉你！」大媽先裝作狂咳幾下，然後說「我趕時間呀」企圖離開，被警員所阻，大媽惱羞成怒，施展「虎尾腳」踢向警員，最終被警員反鎖雙手帶走。大媽被捕時大嗌：「差人打人呀！」但大部份途人均不值其所為，群起指摘。警方回應指當時一名48歲姓陳女子情緒激動，用手及腳襲擊兩名警員，造成兩警手腳受傷送院，事後涉襲警被捕。"},{"pid":"d5556b80246a46c528498541731b8185196a073e","tid":1030313,"uid":45613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:45:38.000Z","msg":"但大部份途人均不值其所為，群起指摘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef22b6c530c72ea653ff01469900d25932849a9","tid":1030313,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:47:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fc854576b1b0af994f963663aa14dfe0ae18e90","tid":1030313,"uid